851
00:47:36.699 --> 00:47:39.354
<i>Jika itu mungkin.</i>

852
00:47:48.798 --> 00:47:50.060
<i>Aku akan segera pergi.</i>

853
00:47:50.887 --> 00:47:52.541
sebenarnya aku tak mau, tapi...

854
00:47:53.977 --> 00:47:55.631
sepertinya aku harus pergi.

